        </span>
       	  <span id="edit_del_6704701"></span>
          <div class="tag">
          <span>作者：<a href="http://xueluowuyin.bokee.com"><span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
<span itemprop="name">梅雪飘飘</span></span></a></span><span itemprop="datePublished" content="2008-05-06 21:27">2008-05-06 21:27</span><span>分类：<a href="http://xueluowuyin.bokee.com/category/0/1">默认分类</a></span><span>标签：
                    </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cnt">
         	<!--  -->
          	<div class="txt"><span itemprop="articleBody">
            when you say nothing at all（尽在不言中）It's amazing how you can speak right to my heartWithout saying a word, you can light up the darkTry as I may, I could never explainWhat I hear when you don't say a thing Krauss AlisonThe smile on your face lets me know that you need meThere's a truth in your eyes saying you'll never leave meThe touch of your hand says you'll catch me if ever I fallYou say it best when you say nothing at allAll day long I can hear people talking out loudBut when you hold me near, you drown out the crowdOld Mr. Webster could never defineThe smile on your face lets me know that you need meThere's a truth in your eyes saying you'll never leave meThe touch of your hand says you'll catch me if ever I fallYou say it best when you say nothing at allThe smile on your face lets me know that you need meThere's a truth in your eyes saying you'll never leave meThe touch of your hand says you'll catch me if ever I fallYou say it best when you say nothing at all2008-03          	</span></div>
        </div>
